angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64369653fc58606cf8523e7174b0999ce46f6dd","tid":304474,"uid":8632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都係好事<br />\n證明連登仔對財務公司有介心<br />\n<br />\n見樓主咁慘 幫手推post<br />\n你見過最誇張爭人幾多錢？"},{"pid":"d957a4827b7ed409d11e41d109031e3380cecfb0","tid":304474,"uid":2078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都係好事<br />\n證明連登仔對財務公司有介心<br />\n<br />\n見樓主咁慘 幫手推post<br />\n你見過最誇張爭人幾多錢？</blockquote><br />\nThanks,不過咁冷清，係我預料之外，果然連登仔個個都百萬年薪<br />\n<br />\n無話最誇張既，做得耐好麻目啦，以前初做果陣都會記得d客既名既<br />\n<br />\n兩球幾，drp <br />\n<br />\nIva既話，三千幾萬"},{"pid":"9897cd39c5fdcb76244ff6c4f01928d95bce4e59","tid":304474,"uid":2078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都係好事<br />\n證明連登仔對財務公司有介心<br />\n<br />\n見樓主咁慘 幫手推post<br />\n你見過最誇張爭人幾多錢？</blockquote><br />\n個post我應該會棄嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 都無人問"},{"pid":"f46c943622a1b59e470450265b54e6c06670480b","tid":304474,"uid":33220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"13萬倒 想自己還 唔想問屋企<br />\n月入16k 現有40k cash<br />\n3條出左街 分別40k,20k<br />\n仲有條gymroom 大概5k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點搞"},{"pid":"968cba941835437fc61b0533f92cf62a87a4aef1","tid":304474,"uid":55979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有18萬財仔<br />\n11萬係銀行+信用卡<br />\n月入13k<br />\n<br />\n可以點？</blockquote><br />\n財仔係邊幾間？<br />\n銀行+信用卡係邊幾間</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5a538ea52e69949a7fbe1a32238170a9c50880","tid":304474,"uid":2078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>13萬倒 想自己還 唔想問屋企<br />\n月入16k 現有40k cash<br />\n3條出左街 分別40k,20k<br />\n仲有條gymroom 大概5k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點搞</blockquote><br />\n做唔到，倍數太低<br />\n你試左結餘轉戶先，如果唔肯做，先有得大條道理同佢地做"},{"pid":"6ffed0751549837d3b04d9f5b6590077489fc0fd","tid":304474,"uid":2078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有18萬財仔<br />\n11萬係銀行+信用卡<br />\n月入13k<br />\n<br />\n可以點？</blockquote><br />\n財仔係邊幾間？<br />\n銀行+信用卡係邊幾間</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做到有餘，首先你齊哂入息証明，獅子依間野一個月入息証明就夠，你同獅子傾掂哂，過程大概半個月到，之後拎埋個agreement 同邦文傾，一定唔好調轉，唔係實傾唔到"},{"pid":"a5bdd4d1a4e7f7db6d0e438b2c061339c47bd010","tid":304474,"uid":55979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有18萬財仔<br />\n11萬係銀行+信用卡<br />\n月入13k<br />\n<br />\n可以點？</blockquote><br />\n財仔係邊幾間？<br />\n銀行+信用卡係邊幾間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做到有餘，首先你齊哂入息証明，獅子依間野一個月入息証明就夠，你同獅子傾掂哂，過程大概半個月到，之後拎埋個agreement 同邦文傾，一定唔好調轉，唔係實傾唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來可以自己傾債務重組？請指教<br />\n<br />\n因出糧戶口已經在HSBC<br />\n就咁入hsbc，同佢講想債務重組？<br />\n定有咩途徑？<br />\n要唔要同佢講仲有邦民數？<br />\n<br />\n同hsbc搞掂後, 邦民都係自已同佢去傾？"},{"pid":"f628bc02b913a064d25566f5ee7fb399fc734f31","tid":304474,"uid":33220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>13萬倒 想自己還 唔想問屋企<br />\n月入16k 現有40k cash<br />\n3條出左街 分別40k,20k<br />\n仲有條gymroom 大概5k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點搞</blockquote><br />\n做唔到，倍數太低<br />\n你試左結餘轉戶先，如果唔肯做，先有得大條道理同佢地做</blockquote><br />\n咩叫倍數<br />\n結餘轉戶姐係借錢還卡數